! Google search
google.*##.xFNJP
google.*##fsr > a.Fx4vi:nth-child(2)
google.*###taw
google.*###rhs
google.*###fsl
google.*###gws-product_ads__pla-dnsrc
google.*##fsr > a.Fx4vi:nth-child(2)
||google.*$cookie
